<p><strong>Working with icons</strong></p>
<p>Many restaurant menus use symbols or icons to indicate that a dish is spicy, a regional favorite, vegetarian, etc. Easy Restaurant Menu Manager WordPress plugin comes with the following icons ready to use: spicy, specially prepared, award-winning, healthy eating choice, new menu item and vegetarian dish. The extended version allows you to edit these and create new ones.</p>
<p>To edit these, or add your own, click on "Item Icons" in the "Manage Menus" area of your dashboard. The recommended size for new icons is 16px by 16px. The icon description will display in a popup tooltip when hovered over, so your site's visitors can easily learn what an icon means.</p>
